{
  "stem": "13471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would take-- the Navy would take recent graduates from college and send them to one of two places, either Northwestern University or that old battleship in New York called the Prairie State, and give them a 90-day quick brush-up on navigation, and seamanship, and so forth, and boom-- send them out to sea.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But for us who had already been commissioned into the Navy-- by this time, I had a whole year, you see, in the Navy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was an old veteran.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They had a special shortened version of that, of 60 days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I wasn't a 90-Day Wonder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was a 60-Day Wonder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, I learned a lot that was very useful, and I was very grateful for it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, I learned night seamanship, you know, everything about navigation, and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I learned-- And so then they sent me out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they sent me to Boston-- Boston Harbor, as a fifth wheel on a mine-sweep, just to get a little sea doing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I learned a lot about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then they sent me as Prospective Commanding Officer to an APc, which was essentially a Boston fishing dragger hull-- wood-- diesel propelled, three officers and 21 crew.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were supposed to carry small detachments of Navy-- Army in inner island [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] invasions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could carry 80 men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is what I was supposed to be doing, you see?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Were you still an ensign?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was still an ensign, en-sigh-gan, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My first-- my first-- I went to the-- the ship was being built in Warren, Rhode Island.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And boy, if you want a perfect little mini-Massachusetts, New England town, that is still just gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a great time.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
